SQL_STMT_U.val: select cast (count ( DISTINCT DEBC_DEBH ) as decimal (18,2)) from :1/debb left join :1/clnt on DEBB_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and DEBB_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO left join :1/debc on DEBB_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO AND DEBC_DATDELETED IS NULL left join :1/dcmc on DEBB_DEBC_NO = DCMC_DEBC_NO where CLNT104_LEGAL_ADMNO = :2 and CLNT104_LEGAL_CLNTNO = :3 and ( DEBB_ACTINVAFACACCH <>0 or VALUE(DCMC_SPECIALACCOUNTH,0) <> 0 ) ;
select cast ( sum (VALUE ( DCMC_SPECIALACCOUNTH, 0) ) as decimal (13,2) ) from :1/dcmc where DCMC_MARK_CODE = 909 and DCMC_ADMNO = :2 and DCMC_CLNTNO = :3 ;
select cast (sum ( DEBC_CREDITLIMITH ) as decimal (18,2)) from :1/debc where DEBC_ADMNO = :2 and DEBC_CLNTNO = :3 and DEBC_DATDELETED IS NULL ;
select cast (count ( * ) as decimal (18,2)) from :1/debc where DEBC_ADMNO = :2 and DEBC_CLNTNO = :3 AND DEBC_DATDELETED IS NULL and value ( DEBC_CREDITLIMITH , 0 ) > 0
select cast ( sum (DEBB_ACTINVAFACACCH) as decimal (13,2) ) from :1/debb where DEBB_ADMNO = :2 and DEBB_CLNTNO = :3 ;

select CAST ( SUM ( MIN ( MAX ( VALUE ( ( select sum (VALUE ( DCMC_SPECIALACCOUNTH, 0) ) from :1/dcmc where DCMC_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO ) , 0 ) + value ( DEBB_ACTINVAFACACCH, 0) , 0 ) , VALUE ( DEBC_CREDITLIMIT, 0) )) AS DECIMAL (13,2)) , CAST ( SUM ( MAX ( VALUE ( ( select sum (VALUE ( DCMC_SPECIALACCOUNTH, 0) ) from :1/dcmc where DCMC_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO ), 0 ) + value ( DEBB_ACTINVAFACACCH, 0) - VALUE ( DEBC_CREDITLIMIT, 0) , 0 ) +MIN ( VALUE ( ( select sum (VALUE ( DCMC_SPECIALACCOUNTH, 0) ) from :1/dcmc where DCMC_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO ) , 0 ) + value ( DEBB_ACTINVAFACACCH, 0) , 0 ) ) AS DECIMAL (13,2) ) from :1/debc left join :1/debb on DEBB_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO where DEBC_ADMNO = :2 and DEBC_CLNTNO = :3 AND DEBC_DATDELETED IS NULL ;

select CAST ( SUM ( MAX ( VALUE ( ( select sum (VALUE ( DCMC_SPECIALACCOUNTH, 0) ) from :1/dcmc where DCMC_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO ), 0 ) + value ( DEBB_ACTINVAFACACCH, 0) - VALUE ( DEBC_CREDITLIMIT, 0) , 0 ) +MIN ( VALUE ( ( select sum (VALUE ( DCMC_SPECIALACCOUNTH, 0) ) from :1/dcmc where DCMC_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO ) , 0 ) + value ( DEBB_ACTINVAFACACCH, 0) , 0 ) ) AS DECIMAL (13,2) ) from :1/debc left join :1/debb on DEBB_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO where DEBC_ADMNO = :2 and DEBC_CLNTNO = :3 AND DEBC_DATDELETED IS NULL AND VALUE ( DEBC_CREDITLIMIT, 0) > 0 ;
DELETE FROM :1/RADA WHERE RADA_ID_CLIENT = :2 and RADA_PERIOD = :3

select cast ( sum (DEBB_ACTINVAFACACCH) as decimal (13,2) ), cast ( sum (VALUE ( DCMC_SPECIALACCOUNTH, 0) ) as decimal (13,2) ) , cast ( sum (DEBC_CREDITLIMITH) as decimal (13,2) ) , cast ( sum (DEBC_FINANCELIMITH ) as decimal (13,2) ) , cast ( DEBB_DEBC_NO as decimal (9,0) ) , cast ( DEBC_DEBH as decimal (9,0 ) ) , cast ( DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH as decimal (9,0) ) , cast ( sum (DEBB_ACTINVAFACACCH + VALUE(DCMC_SPECIALACCOUNTH,0) ) as decimal (13,2)) as sum_key from :1/debb left join :1/dcmc on DEBB_DEBC_NO = DCMC_DEBC_NO and DCMC_MARK_CODE = 909 left join :1/debc on DEBB_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO left join :1/debh on DEBC_DEBH = DEBH_NO where DEBB_ADMNO = :2 and DEBB_CLNTNO = :3 group by DEBB_DEBC_NO , DEBC_DEBH , DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH order by sum_key desc FETCH FIRST 10 ROWS ONLY
